Requirement description:
Double-click to edit
The system shall access the necessary
driving modules (ADAS, Autonomous driving)
to take the safety actions
The system shall start communicating
through a Network with surrounding vehicles
To increse the preformance we use sensors like:
IR, Capcitive touch, Smoke, etc..
IR camera to monitor the driver behavior
The system Shall communicate with the sensors
and delivers meaningful data throw sensors drivers
about the driver state
The system shall use a combination
of data about the driver state to provide
more accurate results
The system shall decide the Alarm
level and type based on the environment
The system shall decide
the next action based on the data and equations
The system shall detect and recognize the
unintended behaviors like drowsiness, eye gaze
, distractions, etc..
The system shall enhance the road safety
